{
  "text": "Realizations. In [CITATION_1] it is shown that ATDFs and tag-based ATDFs can be realized from lossy TDFs [CITATION_2] and correlated-product secure TDFs [CITATION_3] , which can be realized from a variety of standard numbertheoretic and lattice-based assumptions. Furthermore, tag-based ATDFs were constructed from a strong but non-decisional (i.e., search) problem on RSA in [CITATION_4] .",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "10388650",
    "[CITATION_2]": "36024007",
